# Theme tokens (light / dark)

Prefer semantic tokens and `.rph-*` utilities from `apps/web/src/app/globals.css`. Do **not** invent new ad-hoc `dark:bg-zinc-*` / `dark:bg-slate-*` stacks on new UI.

## Tokens (Tailwind)

- Surfaces: `bg-rph-page`, `bg-rph-raised`, `bg-rph-chrome`, `bg-rph-elevated`
- Borders: `border-rph-border`, `border-rph-border-strong`
- Text: `text-rph-fg`, `text-rph-fg-secondary`, `text-rph-fg-muted`
- Links: `text-rph-link`, `hover:text-rph-link-hover`
- Brand: `bg-rph-rail`, `text-rph-rail` (sidebar / primary actions)

## Utilities

- `.rph-card` / `.rph-panel` — cards
- `.rph-chrome` — top bars / chrome strips
- `.rph-input` — form fields
- `.rph-btn-primary` / `.rph-btn-ghost`
- `.rph-pill` / `.rph-pill-active` — section pills
- `.rph-h1`, `.rph-muted`, `.rph-link`, `.rph-alert-*`

## When editing older screens

Migrate touched markup to tokens opportunistically; do not big-bang rewrite unrelated files.
